</font></td>
<td valign=top><FONT SIZE="1" COLOR="#9988ff" FACE="Verdana, Arial">posted 11-25-2000 11:33 CT (US) &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="gbadmin.cgi?action=edit&number=28"><IMG SRC="http://www.themiscpage.com/guestbook/trash.gif"  BORDER=0 ALT="Delete This Entry"></A></font> <HR><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Well, I finally got around to looking at your page.  It looks quite nice.  If I ever get around to finishing mine, I'll give you the URL.  Anyway, you know my e-mail address, so I don't feel it necessary to post.  See ya at 2nd round or something.</FONT>
</td></tr>
